title: GCP GCE Disk
agents: gcp
catalog: cloud/gcp
license: GPLv2
distribution: check_mk
description:
 This check monitors GCE discs independent of a vm.
 The check monitors

 - completed read and write operations
 - read and write throughput

 To make this check work you have to configure the related
 special agent {Google Cloud Platform (GCP)}.

discovery:
 One service is created for each disk
